Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.41,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Well... it's about another \Ncompensation lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:05.78,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,The one caught cheating\N was my wife, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:09.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I am Honjo Yayoi-san's legal \Nrepresentative, Karasuma Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:12.26,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,We are suing for five million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:15.96,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Karasuma Keiko is \NHakamada-sensei's ex-lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.29,Default,H,0,0,0,,As I have already explained, \Nhe doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.73,Default,H,0,0,0,,So for this particular case, I think \Nyou should consult a different lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Those aren't Hakamada-sensei's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:27.68,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to help that client,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,the way that you would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.74,Default,H,0,0,0,,I know I'm overstepping \Nmy bounds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,you should be prepared to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.07,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:43.53,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:45.99,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,Hakamada's assistant\N Nonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,We should fight this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:50.06,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Kanae's ex-husband\N Kurasawa Yoshihito
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,We can't take this lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:54.00,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Did Hakamada-sensei change his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:55.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,But, we don't have to rely on him. \NThere are other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:02.62,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What other ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.97,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,There is one indispensable person \Nyou must have on your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:09.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,I need you to convince someone\N to be on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:13.24,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,My side?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:14.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,Your wife, Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.57,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I think that's going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.70,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:23.76,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,we've been living \Nseparately for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.76,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,She hasn't answered my calls \Nsince we last saw each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:29.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:36.22,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.51,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Kanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.52,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,Evidence of adultery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.01,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.94,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,We gather evidence that will \Ngive us the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:50.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm looking for evidence that \Nwill give us the advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,of when the affair started...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.45,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,the days and times of the trysts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:55.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,and if possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.35,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,maybe even the number of times he's \Nhad physical relationships with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.70,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:04.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,For example, check \NShiori-san's car's GPS history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:06.26,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori doesn't even have \Na driver's license.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:07.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:09.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,her cell phone and PC email history..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.65,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,She took her cell and laptop with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:18.21,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Is evidence like that going \Nto help us at this stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:20.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:24.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,but if we can get details about the affair, \Nwe might find a way to counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:27.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Can I look in Shiori-san's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:27.98,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:31.32,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,You're very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:35.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,You can get lots of information \Nfrom a single dinner receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:39.02,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Is this the kind of thing you did \Nwhen you and I got divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:41.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sort of, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.00,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,You've become strong, Kanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:47.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.31,Bengoshi-Credits_Center,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Yoshihito's wife\N Kurasawa Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.31,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.38,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Why are you snooping in my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.99,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.28,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I thought it was weird
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:05.18,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,that you went to that\N Hakamada lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.26,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's because you wanted\N to see each other, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:09.62,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I've had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.68,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori. Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.36,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.67,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Kanae was looking \Nfor evidence for our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.69,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:19.40,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,And what good will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:21.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,We need whatever information we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:25.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll have to pay \Nthe amount they've set.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:31.00,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I don't care any more how \Nmuch the compensation fee is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:31.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.41,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} should pay the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.73,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's all your fault, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:42.32,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,You said you'd make all my wishes \Ncome true if I married you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.68,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,You said you were going \Nto make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.92,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,But you had to pay that \Nwoman's compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.60,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,and because of that, \Nmy life is a disappointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.72,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,If I'd known this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:59.27,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I never would've married you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're completely full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Whenever you open your mouth, \Nyou only talk about money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:18.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,You were there with Yoshihito-san \Nwhen you got slapped with the lawsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,You saw the anguish on \Nhis face, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,Didn't you feel anything for him at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:30.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be aware of the \Nserious consequences of adultery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:41.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,The first thing an adulterer \Nmust do is apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:45.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,And the second thing they \Nmust do is apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,The third is more of the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,You have to keep on apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:56.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,However, as far as I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,you haven't asked Yoshihito-san's \Nforgiveness even once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,You don't even try to learn\N from your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.68,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Of all the men I have ever met...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.89,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,you are a "dumb man" \Nof the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,Of all the people I've met...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.68,Default,K,0,0,0,,you are a dumb woman\N of the highest order,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:23.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,the reigning idiot queen\N of all other dumb women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,But, even someone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,is still precious to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yoshihito-san said he doesn't \Nwant to divorce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.17,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,He said he wants to start over, \Nand have a good marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.44,Default,K,0,0,0,,What matters to you the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Give it some serious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.34,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why must his ex-wife do \Nall the talking for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.18,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,The first time he seduced me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.85,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,was at a place called Le Breeze\N in west Azabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:34.89,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.92,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything \Nabout the affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.85,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,If that will help our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.58,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:58.12,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.27,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.66,Bengoshi-Phone_Fujisawa,Call contact,0,0,0,,Fujisawa Yoshihito
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.76,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,It's Yoshihito.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sorry I sort of lost it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.56,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.14,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, Shiori told me \Nabout the man she was seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:26.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.34,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I'm relaying the information to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.57,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Can you write it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:37.99,Bengoshi-Kanae_Notes,Notebook top part,0,0,0,,The first time they met was at Le Breeze \N(French restaurant) in west Azabu. \N October: She doesn't remember the day of\N the week, but Takashi-san asked her out again. \NFor about six months afterward, they met \N3 or 4 times a month at various times, and \Nsometimes more often, even once a week, \Nin Daikanyama, Shibuya, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:42.06,Bengoshi-Credits_Center,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Attorney\N Hakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.46,Default,H,0,0,0,,Good work on the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.92,Default,H,0,0,0,,I can launch a counterattack\N with this material.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.86,Default,H,0,0,0,,I need some more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.67,Default,H,0,0,0,,Will you please call \NYoshihito-san and Shiori-san here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:09.74,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N {\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:14.92,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption right,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Final Episode\N The Battle of Fate Between Attorneys! The Final Outcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:18.96,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I'm being sued for compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.09,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.13,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,He must've found some kind of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:24.10,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Sieg Law Office attorney\N Karasuma Keiko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.20,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Any idea what it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.45,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.00,Bengoshi-Credits_Takashi,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Shiori's illicit partner\N Honjo Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:30.72,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I always followed your instructions \Ncarefully whenever I saw Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.14,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There should be no problem, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.34,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Well, it's not anything \NI wasn't expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.68,Bengoshi-Credits_Yayoi,Caption,0,0,0,,Takashi's wife\N Honjo Yayoi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.69,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,When we first met each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:45.08,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Takashi-san said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.37,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,"My marriage is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.69,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Our divorce is a matter of time."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.96,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Then, after we started seeing each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.42,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,"I reconciled with my wife recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.50,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,We might not divorce, but do \Nyou still want to see me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.70,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,He asked me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.68,Default,H,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:14.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,There's a high possibility Karasuma\N was advising him at that juncture.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,Advising him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.68,Default,H,0,0,0,,This is only a conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.63,Default,H,0,0,0,,but Honjo Takashi-san's \Nrelationship to his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.05,Default,H,0,0,0,,was already in ruins from \Nbefore he met Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:30.17,Default,H,0,0,0,,They may have already \Nbeen discussing divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:35.33,Default,H,0,0,0,,Takashi-san would have then consulted\N his company's advising attorney, Karasuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.41,Default,H,0,0,0,,She likely advised him to use \Nhis affair with you, Shiori-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.25,Default,H,0,0,0,,to sue you for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:45.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} why he said he \Nreconciled with his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:54.04,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,You better not have acted \Nconspicuously. Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.43,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I've been living my life according \Nto Karasuma-san's instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.22,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:04.74,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:07.89,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,You're getting a divorce \Nlike you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.63,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,But if I can't get a \Nlarge compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.18,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,you're the one who'll get \Nthe brunt of the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.52,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,But that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.17,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,By the way, how did you typically\N keep in contact with Takashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.57,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I mostly just texted him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.98,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,but he used the phone most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.11,Default,H,0,0,0,,That's to avoid a paper trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.24,Default,H,0,0,0,,He must've been following\N instructions from Karasuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:44.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's why the texts looked like \NShiori-san was initiating the trysts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.27,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side,White bubble,0,0,0,,Take me out for lunch today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.27,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side,Green bubble,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:45.53,Default,H,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.40,Default,H,0,0,0,,do you have any photos \N of you and Takashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.99,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:53.95,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Takashi-san said \Nhe didn't like pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,Also by her instructions, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.36,Default,H,0,0,0,,Preparing for the eventual hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:01.15,Default,H,0,0,0,,by ensuring there was no \Ndisadvantageous evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:06.77,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,In other words, he was using \NShiori to get compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:09.99,Default,H,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.05,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,So, that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:14.63,Default,H,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:17.56,Default,H,0,0,0,,Shiori-san, you need to \Nrecant your illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.34,Default,H,0,0,0,,But, Takashi-san is\N not at all repentant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,Instead, he is trying to transfer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.59,Default,H,0,0,0,,the compensation fee that {\i1}he{\i0} \Nshould be paying to Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:32.19,Default,H,0,0,0,,And Karasuma cannot \Nbe forgiven either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,for having given such \Ninstructions as a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.50,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,The most important thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:45.54,Default,H,0,0,0,,to get evidence that the Honjo \Nmarriage was already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.26,Default,H,0,0,0,,If we can get that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.23,Default,H,0,0,0,,they cannot sue Shiori-san \Nfor compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:54.86,Default,H,0,0,0,,And in turn, it makes it possible \Nfor us to sue them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.48,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,It sounds like it's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.84,Bengoshi-Credits_Center,Caption,0,0,0,,Freelance Investigator\N Umemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:58.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,Kurumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.02,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Looks like Sensei came \Nback to his senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.37,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Which means he'd want me\N to do some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.68,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.69,Default,H,0,0,0,,I will personally pay for your services.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.64,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:10.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,And this time, I will lend \Na hand in the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,You will, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:21.16,Default,H,0,0,0,,If the current compensation lawsuit\N is a planned conspiracy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,it will be difficult to find evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.55,Default,H,0,0,0,,Knowing how Karasuma works,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:29.79,Default,H,0,0,0,,there's a high probability that evidence\N is being thoroughly covered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.83,Default,H,0,0,0,,We must go into this battle together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.85,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Don't cramp my style, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.98,Bengoshi-Ressurrection_Marilyn,DVD box-set,0,0,0,,The Resurrection\N of Marilyn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.98,Bengoshi-Spy_Marilyn,DVD box-set,0,0,0,,Iron Spy Woman \N{\b1\c&H7681AC&\3c&H3C3C58&}Marilyn{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.82,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Would you like to borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.62,Default,H,0,0,0,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.61,Default,H,0,0,0,,I have already studied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:48.72,Default,H,0,0,0,,Iron Spy Woman Marilyn, \Nseason 29, episode 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:49.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:54.82,Default,Marilyn,0,0,0,,She who controls information\N controls the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:58.44,Default,H,0,0,0,,She who controls information \Ncontrols the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.46,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Why didn't you let me say it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei is fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.12,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.80,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,One fried chicken lunch, \Nand one seaweed lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:14.29,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.21,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.56,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.98,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Are both of you employed \Nat Honjo Industries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.08,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,You know where we work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:22.28,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.58,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,It's rumored the men who \Nwork there are gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.62,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.57,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,And that president Honjo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.33,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,He's got that mature, awesome look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.78,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Might he be single?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.05,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,The president's married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.04,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,He's a notorious womanizer, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.90,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,I wouldn't recommend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.37,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Oh? Like how?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.04,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,For example—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.04,Bengoshi-Overlap,Office stiff2,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.32,Default,Office stiff2,0,0,0,,You're talking about \Nour president, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.62,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,Whoops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.40,Default,Office stiff,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.01,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.41,Default,Office stiff3,0,0,0,,I hear they're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.68,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Excuse me, one fried chicken lunch, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.25,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kur,0,0,0,,Yes, here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.92,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,No, I don't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.59,Bengoshi-Honjo_Sign,Plaque,0,0,0,,Honjo
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.86,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.72,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,The Honjos are getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:58.72,Default,Lady2,0,0,0,,I heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.45,Default,Lady2,0,0,0,,I knew it was coming, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:04.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,What? They're getting a divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.92,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:09.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,We're newlyweds looking \Nfor a place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,Their home was up for sale, \Nso we went to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.44,Default,Lady2,0,0,0,,Well, how about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,But they're moving out \Nbecause of a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sounds like bad luck,\N doesn't it, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.53,Default,H,0,0,0,,My wife is fussy \Nabout things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.43,Default,H,0,0,0,,Do you know the reason why \Nthey're getting a divorce?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.50,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,I heard it's because the \Nhusband cheated on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?! He was cheating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:33.62,Default,H,0,0,0,,Cheating? Recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.00,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,That man? He's been \Nplaying around for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.59,Default,Lady2,0,0,0,,Shh, Yamamoto-san, we\N can't talk about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.88,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.16,Default,Lady1,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,They sure are thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,They've even shut up \Nthe local housewives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.53,Default,H,0,0,0,,That's typical for Karasuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.65,Default,H,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, please have a \Ndiscussion with Kurumi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,and find another method \Nof investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,And what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.47,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'm going to investigate \Nthis area a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:03.38,Default,H,0,0,0,,I have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.42,Default,K,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:05.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:10.62,Default,H,0,0,0,,You can let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:21.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,What do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where can I go get evidence that \Nthis couple's marriage was over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.34,Bengoshi-Credits_Center,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Cafe waitress\N Mizutani Sara
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.54,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.99,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:40.72,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I... don't like being pressured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.45,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.32,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,You are thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:53.16,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,"This gal is useless."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.68,Default,K,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.36,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,You're being watched?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:15.53,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:19.17,Default,Yahoi,0,0,0,,There was a tall man wearing glasses\N in front of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:23.53,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That probably was Hakamada,\N our opposing attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.44,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.52,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.50,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,As long as you have me as your lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:35.05,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,the other party's lawyer is \Nstrictly forbidden by law
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.34,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,from contacting you \N without my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.13,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,If he broke that law,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.72,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,he will disbarred by \Nthe bar association.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:46.52,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,You haven't done anything \Nconspicuous, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:50.92,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I haven't left the house other \Nthan to go grocery shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.35,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I'm doing my usual household chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:54.92,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.36,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:00.18,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,How much longer must\N I continue like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.56,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Just a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.88,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,"A little longer" meaning when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.10,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Stop complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:07.25,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,All you have to do is obey \Nour instructions. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:10.48,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.30,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.58,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,She can't go against my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.38,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:26.01,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I heard someone was asking \Nmy employees about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:31.34,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,It would affect their work performance \Nif rumors about me were to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.90,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Is there anything you \Ncould do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.75,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There are ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:38.94,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,to shut them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:46.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:50.15,Default,K,0,0,0,,Here's a tentative investigation \Nreport from Kurumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,They're definitely being thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,Supposedly, there are rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:57.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,that Takashi-san is a womanizer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,and that he's cheated with women\N other than Shiori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,But there's no definitive evidence, \Nand no one will go into detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:05.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.28,Default,H,0,0,0,,they've being covering things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,We won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.73,Default,H,0,0,0,,Let's continue with our investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.50,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Sorry to barge in unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Karasuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:19.58,Default,H,0,0,0,,Can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.78,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Oh, don't make such a stern face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.01,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I've come here to give \Nyou some news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:30.88,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Since we cannot get consent \Nfor the compensation lawsuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.74,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,we are filing an action,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.58,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and will take the matter to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.78,Default,H,0,0,0,,Taking it to court?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:42.74,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Your client, Yoshihito-san, \Nhas already filed a suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.87,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Most likely, the two \Nhearings will converge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "converge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:19:00.81,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word,Orange caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Converged hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:19:00.81,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,White caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Holding a hearing in a single trial concerning the demands of both the plaintiff and the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:51.84,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,It means holding one trial to judge \Nseveral conflicting demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.24,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,Simply put,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.99,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,it's a court battle of \Nour compensation lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:59.40,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,and their compensation lawsuit, \Nall at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.71,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:01.92,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Can you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.98,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Since we're taking it to court,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:07.50,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,you won't have a leg to stand on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,if you have no evidence to present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.06,Default,H,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.62,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.79,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,We'll see you in court, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Go easy on me, Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,She's so arrogant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,It seems she's quite confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:34.48,Default,K,0,0,0,,But you have a secret plan, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.10,Default,H,0,0,0,,Secret plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,You said, "You don't need \Nto worry about that."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.18,Default,H,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:43.33,Default,H,0,0,0,,I just said that because I was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:46.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, you have nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:47.92,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:50.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,For now, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.53,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:01.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:06.66,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,There's a bartender who says he saw\N Takashi-san and Shiori-san on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.42,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Can you come here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.11,Default,H,0,0,0,,We'll be there right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.09,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.25,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,No mistake, it was these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.94,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,I myself took an\N interest in her at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.16,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,because she's my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.88,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Then, this man showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:23.50,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,I heard him say, "If you go out with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.06,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,I'll take you to Tahiti, \Nthe Maldives, anywhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.26,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,He started coming onto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.72,Default,H,0,0,0,,And how did the lady respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:35.77,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,She seemed happy about it, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:40.64,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,But, she expressed worry that his wife \Nmight find out if they went on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.07,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,And what did the man say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.92,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,He said, "Even if she finds out,\N there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.34,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,"Our marriage is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:54.52,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time \Nbefore we get divorced."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,That sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.60,Default,H,0,0,0,,Are you certain he said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.94,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:04.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Would you be willing \Nto testify in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.71,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:07.67,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,I think we scored, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.68,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You can win at the hearing now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:14.99,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.98,Bengoshi-Court,Plaque,0,0,0,,Court of Law
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.80,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,What happens when hearings converge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,This time around,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:30.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,the first case will concern the compensation lawsuit\N of Yoshihito-san against Takashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:34.09,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,So, Yoshihito-san is the \Nplaintiff in the first case,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:38.60,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition_Top,Caption top,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Kurasawa Yoshihito (represented by Hakamada) {\c&H2FEAEB&\b1}→{\b0} {\c&HB4542A&\3c&HFEDAD7&}first case plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:38.60,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition_Bottom,Caption bottom,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Honjo Takashi (represented by  Karasuma) {\b1\c&H20E7EE&}→{\b0} {\c&H1A009F&\3c&HCDCEFA&}first case defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:37.06,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,and Takashi-san is the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.59,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:42.63,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,So, Yayoi-san's lawsuit against \NShiori-san is the second case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:46.17,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition_Top,Caption top,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}Hojo Yayoi (represented by Karasuma) {\c&H2FEAEB&\b1}→{\b0} {\c&HB4542A&\3c&HFEDAD7&}second case plaintiff
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:46.17,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition_Bottom,Caption bottom,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)}{\fs21}Kurasawa Shiori (represented by Hakamada)  {\b1\c&H20E7EE&}→{\b0} {\c&H1A009F&\3c&HCDCEFA&}second case defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.33,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:46.52,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Both sides admit to illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.84,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,So, in this case, the \Ncrucial point of argument
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.97,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,is whether the Honjos' marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:57.12,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\c&HC6461C&\3c&HFFECD9&}Main point of the hearing{\c\3c} {\b1\c&H25EDF2&}→{\c\b0} Was the Honjos' \Nmarriage already broken prior to the illicit affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:53.57,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,was already torn apart \Nbefore the illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:56.54,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,Awesome, Kanae-san. You know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.24,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:22:00.68,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I did a lot of studying for this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.60,Default,H,0,0,0,,Regarding the couple \Nyou saw at the bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,They were Shiori-san there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,and Takashi-san there, is this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:17.06,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:22.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please share with the court what \Nyou heard of their conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:26.88,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,The man seemed a little tipsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:29.29,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,And he came on to the lady, \Nwith offers to take her on trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:32.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,And how did Shiori-san respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.68,0:22:36.66,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,She said, "You have a wife, \Nwon't you get in trouble?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.90,Default,H,0,0,0,,And how did Takashi-san respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.98,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,He replied, "It doesn't \Nmatter if she finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:44.48,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Our marriage is over."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:45.50,Default,H,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:48.71,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,He said, "It's only a matter \Nof time before we're divorced."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.25,0:22:54.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,From this testimony we can clearly see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:22:59.37,Default,H,0,0,0,,that Takashi-san and Yayoi-san's \Nmarriage was already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.76,0:23:03.88,Default,H,0,0,0,,And even if his words were \Nlies to seduce Shiori-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:06.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,Shiori-san, who believed his words,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.97,Default,H,0,0,0,,is not liable to pay for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:10.68,Default,H,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:16.36,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I have been to the bar \Nyou work at, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:19.10,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It is a very nice place, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:21.13,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.73,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:25.10,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,this is what it looks like inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:27.12,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:31.21,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,they keep the lights extremely low,\N in order to create ambience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:36.07,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It is difficult to see \Nwho is in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:38.85,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,And yet, you claim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:42.28,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,that despite this and the fact that \Nyou've never met these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:45.42,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,you still can identify their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.48,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.48,0:23:50.35,Default,H,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:54.23,Default,H,0,0,0,,The defense's statement is mere speculation—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:54.23,Bengoshi-Overlap,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:23:59.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I have definitive proof that the witness \Nwas unable to hear any couple's conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.61,0:24:05.02,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,What day and what month did Takashi-san \Nand Shiori-san meet at the bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:08.69,Default,H,0,0,0,,It was October 17th.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:16.41,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I borrowed the shift schedule \Nfrom the bar's proprietor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:19.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,On October 17th,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:25.62,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Suho-san here was not at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:25.63,Bengoshi-October_Latter,Schedule,0,0,0,,Latter half of October\N {\b0}{\fs24}Heisei 26{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:25.63,Bengoshi-Suho_Schedule,Schedule,0,0,0,,Suho
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:25.63,Bengoshi-Friday_Off,Schedule,0,0,0,,Friday    {\c&H444075&}Day Off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.38,0:24:26.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:28.20,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:31.70,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Couples with age differences \Nare not at all uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.70,0:24:35.73,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This means you saw another \Ncouple on another day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.21,0:24:38.38,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and got them mixed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:43.50,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,Well, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.50,0:24:44.54,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:45.75,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Have some resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:46.76,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:48.25,Default,H,0,0,0,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.78,0:24:51.14,Default,H,0,0,0,,You saw photos of Takashi-san and Shiori-san
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:53.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,and claimed there was no mistake\N they were who you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.76,0:24:58.42,Default,Bartender,0,0,0,,But, like this lady says, \Nit's a dark bar, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.92,0:24:59.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.28,0:25:01.43,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Based on this testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.96,0:25:05.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,there is no evidence that Takashi-san \Nand Yayoi-san's marriage was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.98,0:25:07.94,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.72,0:25:23.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Damn, she got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.65,0:25:25.58,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,That witness was in cahoots with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.78,0:25:26.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,In cahoots?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.14,0:25:29.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,If we found strong evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.65,0:25:31.56,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,we wouldn't need to \Ninvestigate any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.56,0:25:35.42,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,That's how they set it up, and used him\N to play the unreliable witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.33,0:25:39.75,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,I can't believe I fell \Ninto such an obvious trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.96,0:25:57.04,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.49,0:25:59.73,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,There's still time before \Nthe next hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.73,0:26:02.10,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,May I continue the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.59,0:26:04.61,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.30,0:26:07.62,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.97,0:26:11.56,Default,H,0,0,0,,I am going to investigate, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:13.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.04,0:26:15.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.32,0:26:33.38,Default,Deliverer,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.38,0:26:34.74,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Thank you for the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:37.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,You are Honjo Yayoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.09,0:26:38.97,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.45,0:26:40.93,Default,H,0,0,0,,May I have a word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:44.60,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:46.44,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.71,0:26:49.22,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Please contact Karasuma-san instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.68,0:26:52.70,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Aren't you forbidden by law \Nfrom contacting me without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.77,0:26:54.58,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.47,0:26:57.17,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to be disbarred for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.64,0:27:03.34,Default,H,0,0,0,,Regardless, I must \Nknow your side of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.27,0:27:07.74,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Please, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.76,0:27:16.43,Bengoshi-Court2,Sign,0,0,0,,Court of Law
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.62,0:27:23.36,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,I feel pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.85,0:27:27.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,I couldn't find a single \Npiece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.28,0:27:30.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,All we can do now is believe \Nin Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.81,0:27:31.59,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.20,0:27:33.35,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know it'll turn out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.14,0:27:37.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,The bread he baked yesterday \Nwas absolutely awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.94,0:27:43.08,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,What you see here are\N photographs of the Honjo couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.62,0:27:49.63,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,They are even known by their neighbors \Nto be an intimately loving couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.63,0:27:52.03,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You liar. Not a single \Nperson said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.59,0:27:55.10,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,They would take trips \Noverseas every six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.10,0:27:57.22,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,They dined at restaurants\N twice a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.86,0:28:02.70,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,They have many rules between them \Nto support their sense of marital bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.53,0:28:06.27,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Such a happy couple, and yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.56,0:28:09.24,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,because of one woman, they were \Ntorn apart six months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.53,0:28:14.01,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That woman, Shiori-san, who sits there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.72,0:28:15.78,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.14,0:28:18.40,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Takashi-san was the one who initiated—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.64,0:28:20.33,Bengoshi-Overlap,Keiko,0,0,0,,There is no question, clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:22.45,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,that Shiori-san aggressively seduced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.38,0:28:25.44,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Looking at their texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.85,0:28:28.76,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It is clear from these that \NShiori-san was the active initiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:30.10,Bengoshi-Shiori_Name_Text,Text snapshot top,0,0,0,,Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:30.10,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side2,Shiori's Texts,0,0,0,,Takashi-san r u free next week?? \N\N\N I want us to go to Yokohama next time <3 There's a super yummy pancake place there. \N\N\NTake me out for lunch today
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:30.10,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side2,Takashi's Texts,0,0,0,,Yes.\N\N\N Understood.\N\N\N Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.34,0:28:30.67,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,But those texts...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.67,0:28:32.65,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.03,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please, you must calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:38.22,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This evidence tells the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.06,0:28:43.91,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Shiori-san tore apart the \Nhappy Honjo marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.25,0:28:46.86,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and stole the smile \Noff Yayoi-san's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.38,0:28:50.58,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It is only natural that she \Nshould pay for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.80,0:28:53.26,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,That woman really pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.26,0:28:54.68,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,It's all outright lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.93,0:28:56.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,But, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.84,0:29:00.91,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.58,0:29:08.94,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.33,0:29:10.57,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Can anything be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.91,0:29:13.70,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.16,0:29:19.74,Default,H,0,0,0,,What you have presented is \Ncompletely erroneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.92,0:29:25.14,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,And on what do you base your assertion?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:29.39,Default,H,0,0,0,,This was not the first time Takashi-san \Nengaged in an illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.20,0:29:33.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,He has had adulterous affairs \Nseveral times with other partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.83,0:29:36.02,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Please present the \Nbasis for your assertions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.02,0:29:37.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,And every time he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.48,0:29:41.20,Default,H,0,0,0,,he deeply hurt his wife \NYayoi-san's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.47,0:29:45.35,Default,H,0,0,0,,Their marriage was already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.35,0:29:46.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Your Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.53,0:29:48.90,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,the plaintiff is speaking \Nfrom sheer conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.38,0:29:52.54,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Counselor, please clarify \Nthe basis for your assertions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.53,0:29:55.77,Default,H,0,0,0,,I have no basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.20,0:29:57.17,Default,H,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.17,0:30:00.85,Default,H,0,0,0,,there is one witness who can expose \NTakashi-san's past illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.02,0:30:02.49,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.49,0:30:03.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,What witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.53,0:30:08.84,Default,H,0,0,0,,Honjo Takashi-san's wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.83,0:30:12.12,Default,H,0,0,0,,Honjo Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.54,0:30:16.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.56,0:30:18.16,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,What's this guy babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.57,0:30:21.78,Default,H,0,0,0,,I request to question Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.99,0:30:23.40,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Question?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.91,0:30:26.94,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,He has requested to question \NYayoi-san directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.21,0:30:28.58,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Counselor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.58,0:30:29.78,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,what is your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.78,0:30:32.05,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There is no need for that whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.24,0:30:33.77,Default,H,0,0,0,,It is necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.77,0:30:36.63,Default,H,0,0,0,,to prove that Yayoi-san's relationship to \Nher husband was already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.63,0:30:41.14,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Are you hoping Yayoi-san would state \Nsomething that would be disadvantageous to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.14,0:30:41.79,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This is meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.82,0:30:46.05,Default,H,0,0,0,,Meaningless or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.80,0:30:48.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,it is Yayoi-san's decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.79,0:30:50.69,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.16,0:30:53.55,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,you do not have to agree to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.55,0:30:55.64,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This is their ploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.55,0:30:59.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,I want to know your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.46,0:31:01.62,Default,H,0,0,0,,If you let this opportunity pass by,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.12,0:31:04.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,you will end up a mere bystander.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.14,0:31:10.18,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Can you live with ending up\N as a mere bystander?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.52,0:31:16.84,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,This trial is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:18.38,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,It will determine your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.03,0:31:23.04,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,But, even from the very first conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.51,0:31:27.00,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,I felt nothing of your true will.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.71,0:31:30.54,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,If you win the trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:33.67,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,you will get compensation from \NTakashi-san's partner in adultery.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.02,0:31:38.88,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,But is that going to heal your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.80,0:31:42.98,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Who is it that you want to \Nreally sue for compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.01,0:31:49.31,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Whose apology is it \Nthat you {\i1}really{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.28,0:31:57.40,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Yayoi, don't breathe a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.07,0:32:00.69,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,All you need to do is keep \Nquiet and do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.69,0:32:03.26,Default,H,0,0,0,,Do you have to do as he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.76,0:32:07.71,Default,H,0,0,0,,You are a victim of his\N illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.98,0:32:20.48,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I will testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.24,0:32:31.30,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,It is as the lawyer said.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.73,0:32:37.24,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Our married life was \Nalready broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.45,0:32:38.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.44,0:32:41.67,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Hey, stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.83,0:32:42.67,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.67,0:32:46.04,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,We were already making steady \Narrangements for a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.67,0:32:50.74,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,This was not the first time\N he had cheated on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.74,0:32:51.73,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:53.60,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Why won't you obey me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.60,0:32:57.30,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Don't think for a minute that\N I'll just do everything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.62,0:33:05.72,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,This man has been seeing other women,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.19,0:33:08.74,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,even from the beginning of our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.69,0:33:12.10,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,And every time he was caught, \Nhe would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:14.30,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,"I won't ever do it again,"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.72,0:33:16.51,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,and lie to appease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.50,0:33:18.69,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,And this pattern repeated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.16,0:33:21.56,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.10,0:33:26.48,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,And all those times, not {\i1}once{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.02,0:33:29.90,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,did he bow and apologize \Nfor what he'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.82,0:33:34.66,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Why must I obey a man like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.89,0:33:40.02,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Why must I pretend I had a happy marriage \Nwith a man like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.53,0:33:53.24,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I am withdrawing my lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.62,0:33:55.78,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.00,0:33:58.06,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,The one that I truly hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.12,0:34:01.49,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,is this man, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.37,0:34:09.62,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Are you certain you with \Nto withdraw the lawsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.36,0:34:12.98,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.64,0:34:17.47,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,Kurasawa Shiori-san, do you \Nagree to this withdrawal?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.82,0:34:22.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.46,0:34:24.27,Default,H,0,0,0,,we agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.77,0:34:33.49,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,This concludes Honjo Yayoi-san's compensation\N lawsuit against Kurasawa Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.39,0:34:40.38,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,The court's decision of compensation \Nlawsuit case of Kurasawa Yoshihito-san
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.93,0:34:45.68,Default,Judge,0,0,0,,versus Honjo Takashi-san will be \Ndelivered April 10, 2015, at 1:15 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.86,0:34:52.00,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Do you know what \Nyou've done to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.04,0:34:56.21,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Now you won't get compensation, \Nand you did it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.34,0:35:03.71,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Your life after divorce\N is going to be a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.55,0:35:07.25,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, that will not be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:11.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san can sue for compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.44,0:35:15.21,Default,H,0,0,0,,from you, Takashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.49,0:35:17.69,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.07,0:35:19.29,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.20,0:35:23.50,Default,H,0,0,0,,You have an obligation \Nto pay restitution
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.66,0:35:26.83,Default,H,0,0,0,,for Yayoi-san's incurred psychological \Ntrauma from your illicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.33,0:35:30.43,Default,H,0,0,0,,And there is compensation \Nwith respect to the divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.55,0:35:32.50,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. Are you joking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.02,0:35:35.46,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I will fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.17,0:35:39.08,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I'm not paying you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.81,0:35:43.58,Default,H,0,0,0,,You can fight all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.80,0:35:46.53,Default,H,0,0,0,,but you don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.22,0:35:51.35,Default,H,0,0,0,,Isn't that so,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.30,0:35:53.34,Default,H,0,0,0,,Karasuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:56.45,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Something's wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.89,0:35:59.13,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Hakamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.82,0:36:03.27,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Did you see Yayoi-san \Nbefore the hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.16,0:36:06.67,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and plant ideas in her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.54,0:36:08.54,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Because if you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:11.14,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,the bar association will disbar you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.46,0:36:16.12,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,No such thing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.99,0:36:18.88,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I did this out of my own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:20.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.86,0:36:22.59,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You're not capable of \Nstanding up for yourself—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.59,0:36:26.37,Default,H,0,0,0,,If you must insist, then show me proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:29.36,Default,H,0,0,0,,Proof is your specialty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.41,0:36:36.49,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Karasuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.07,0:36:40.02,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I am no longer your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.78,0:36:45.73,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Not once did you lend an ear \Nto what I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.82,0:36:50.81,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I cannot entrust my future \Nto such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.34,0:36:53.47,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.83,0:37:08.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,All you thought about was winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.85,0:37:11.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,and you neglected the \Nmost important thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.12,0:37:14.20,Default,H,0,0,0,,the will of your client.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.56,0:37:17.18,Default,H,0,0,0,,And this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.29,0:37:24.19,Default,H,0,0,0,,Well then, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.32,0:37:27.48,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You must be quite \Nsatisfied with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.28,0:37:30.10,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,A splendid victory in court,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.83,0:37:33.58,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and you avenged the grudge \Nyou held for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.30,0:37:36.90,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please don't belittle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.86,0:37:42.03,Default,H,0,0,0,,I did not fight in this hearing \Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.55,0:37:45.86,Default,H,0,0,0,,Then, and even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.58,0:37:51.64,Default,H,0,0,0,,there is only one thing \NI want you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.17,0:37:56.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.64,0:38:00.34,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You couldn't tell from \Nthe hearing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.82,0:38:09.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,There's only one thing you can do\N to someone you've hurt, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.42,0:38:21.78,Default,H,0,0,0,,To celebrate our victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.78,0:38:23.40,Default,H,0,0,0,,I will whip up champagne bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.40,0:38:24.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Champagne bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.65,0:38:27.05,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'll knead champagne into the dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.05,0:38:28.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,It'd be better to have them separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.86,0:38:30.66,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You'll ruin two ingredients at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.77,0:38:47.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,In that case, how about \Nsweet bean bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.01,0:38:50.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'll knead sweet bean into the dough.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.89,0:38:53.00,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,The sweet beans are supposed \Nto be in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.20,0:38:56.34,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Outside_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada\N Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.77,0:38:57.60,Default,H,0,0,0,,Because she has withdrawn the suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.60,0:39:00.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,you no longer have to pay\N compensation, Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.37,0:39:06.45,Default,H,0,0,0,,The property seizures and wage\N garnishments have also been withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.71,0:39:12.92,Default,H,0,0,0,,I am positive the court will approve \NYoshihito-san's lawsuit against Takashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.44,0:39:16.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,This time, it will be \Napproximately one to two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.15,0:39:18.14,Default,H,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.53,0:39:21.99,Default,H,0,0,0,,since they unjustly threatened \Nwith seizure and lawsuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.34,0:39:26.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,Shiori-san can demand compensation \Nfor attorney fees, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.01,0:39:28.76,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,She can make all those demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.97,0:39:31.73,Default,H,0,0,0,,I expect your wedding \Nwill be a great one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:33.53,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.96,0:39:36.54,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything \Nyou've done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.36,0:39:38.85,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.06,0:39:46.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,I pray that you two will never \Nhave to come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:48.28,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.49,0:39:54.30,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to decline \Nthe weekly serial offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.30,0:39:55.10,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.10,0:39:56.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.46,0:39:59.19,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Big chances like that are \Nvery rare, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:02.84,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,My prediction came\N true, as I knew it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.11,0:40:04.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,What prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.09,0:40:05.81,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:07.97,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.47,0:40:10.89,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.68,0:40:13.40,Bengoshi-Flashback,Sara,0,0,0,,You will lose something big, very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.47,0:40:15.13,Bengoshi-Flashback,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.40,0:40:17.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,You were talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.52,0:40:19.21,Default,Sara,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.34,0:40:23.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,But, I don't feel like I've lost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.57,0:40:27.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,I am going to continue working \Nat the Hakamada Law Office,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.22,0:40:28.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,and continue the monthly serial.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.19,0:40:32.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,That is what I want to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.22,0:40:36.12,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,As your editor,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.12,0:40:39.27,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,I promise you I'll make \Nyour work a big hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.92,0:40:42.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thank you for always supporting me. \NI look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.04,0:40:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.96,0:40:45.08,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.59,0:40:48.00,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I've always been thinking this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.62,0:40:52.58,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,You don't have any \Nmysterious powers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.55,0:40:56.67,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.67,0:40:58.97,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,May I have a look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.68,0:41:01.05,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,Please don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.05,0:41:03.65,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,It cost me 3,000 yen online!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.65,0:41:04.39,Bengoshi-Top,Misata,0,0,0,,Cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.39,0:41:06.68,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,This thing is totally suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.68,0:41:07.95,Bengoshi-Top,Sara,0,0,0,,It's not cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.87,0:41:13.49,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, you turned down \Nthe weekly serialization?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.49,0:41:14.66,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,She did.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.66,0:41:16.12,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.12,0:41:20.02,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,But finally, the manga is \Ncoming out in a single volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.09,0:41:21.72,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.72,0:41:23.50,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,Living on royalties, what a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.50,0:41:25.53,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,What percentage do manga \Nillustrators get?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.53,0:41:28.38,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Please don't jump right to money talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.38,0:41:30.50,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,But, I'm on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.50,0:41:35.28,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,The protagonist's reason for becoming\N a divorce lawyer is revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.55,0:41:39.35,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,The story is going to keep \Ngetting better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:42.08,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,And why did he become a divorce lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.73,0:41:44.34,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Because of a past \Nrelationship with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.58,0:41:48.10,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,Because the protagonist is \Nmodeled after Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.60,0:41:49.21,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.37,0:41:51.81,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,But, that wasn't my reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.95,0:41:52.59,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.88,0:41:53.88,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:55.06,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,What? It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.06,0:41:55.78,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.78,0:41:56.94,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.80,0:42:02.14,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,The reason why I became \Na divorce lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.45,0:42:09.49,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}This drama is a work of fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.58,0:42:08.50,Bengoshi-Top,All,0,0,0,,What?!

